AJAX endpoint map for COSSIE Wholesale Inventory and Management System

This file documents the AJAX calls used by assets/js/app.js.

1. POST api/orders.php
   Saves a wholesale order with customer, business type, product, quantity,
   discount and total amount.

2. POST api/payments.php
   Saves payment information for an order number.

3. POST api/returns.php
   Saves rejected goods reports for damaged, expired, wrong, leaking or short
   quantity items.

The JavaScript uses fetch(), which is the modern AJAX method supported by
current browsers.
